civilization /ˌsɪvɪlaɪˈzeɪʃən/

(civilizations) BRIT also  civilisation 

1. N-VAR A civilization is a human society with its own social organization and culture. 文明社会 

例： The ancient civilizations of Central and Latin America were founded upon corn. 中美洲和拉丁美洲的古代文明社会是建立在玉米之上的。 

2. N-UNCOUNT Civilization is the state of having an advanced level of social organization and a comfortable way of life. 文明 

例： ...our advanced state of civilization. …我们高度的文明形态。

